data.description: Country living with acreage! Brick ranch house with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths. There's 2 master bedrooms, one on the main floor and one upstairs. The upstairs master bedroom has a private balcony with views of the back portion of the property and the barn.  There's 2 additional bedrooms upstairs and a full bath.  There's a bonus kitchen with dining area, family room with fireplace, and another family room with a sliding barn door with plenty of natural light that will be great for entertaining family and friends. The main kitchen has custom cabinets with granite countertops and dining area. The laundry room is just off the main kitchen. There's over 5 acres of land with a red barn for your farm animals. The detached building has a workshop area with parking and a separate room for a man cave, office, or convert into a small apartment. This listing is being sold "As Is." Just needs some TLC.
